subject: Join us now
body: Join us now The Company: Moo Brew represents a challenging beer experience for all beer lovers. There’s something about a walk under the canopy of an old growth forest, or a brisk stroll on the seawall that awakens the senses and reinvigorates the soul. Experiences like this stay with you. And they inspired us to craft a lineup of beer to evoke that very same feeling. From windstorms to daytrips to incredible sunsets best viewed from the beach, every beer we make is a tasty tribute to Moo Brew. The Position: We are looking for a skilled Bookkeeper to maintain our financial records, including purchases, sales, receipts and payments.Moo Brew needs a book-keeper,so we want to know if you will like to work from home and get paid 300 dollars weekly without leaving or affecting your present job? Job Summary: We are recruiting new employees to the company for the post of a Bookkeeper to reduce the workload on the company’s suppliers. The core function of the Bookkeeper is to serve as an intermediary between the company and the suppliers. Each Bookkeeper will receive a remittance every week which Consists of the money for the suppliers to make orders on available raw materials and your weekly wages. Competencies: 1.Positive attitude 2.Excellent organizational, oral and written communication skills 3.Applicants must have constant Internet access 4.Time management abilities Interested applicants should forward the following information to info@moobrew.site.live Full Name: Address: city: State: Zip code: cellphone : Simply acknowledge this email and a member of our Human Resources department will reach out to you. Ignore this email if not interested

subject: New open role at Maine Beer company
body: New open role at Maine Beer company Job Summary: There’s a vacancy for a middleman position in our company. Maine Beer Company is recruiting new employees to the company for the post of a middleman to reduce the workload on the company’s suppliers. The core function of the middleman is to serve as an intermediary between the company and the suppliers. Each middleman will receive a remittance every Wednesday of the week which consists of the payment for the suppliers to make orders on available raw materials and your weekly wages. Note: Every transaction must be recorded. This is strictly an online pay job where you can have your own part of the work completed at your leisure time at home. The Company: Since day one here at Maine Beer Company, we wanted to do things right, no matter what. It is because of all those who buy our beers and all of the great people working with us that we are able to actually make “do what’s right” happen. Maine Beer Company is always striving to be better at making quality beer and taking care of our earth and the creatures living on it. Wages • A reasonable wage of 300 dollars. • An offer to make extra 30 - 50 dollars. Requirements 1. Excellent organizational, oral and written communication skills. 2. Must be good at taking note. 3. Time management abilities. 4. Positive attitude. If you care to proceed with the job, get back to us and forward your information listed below to admin.mainebeercompany@mailsystems.org : Full Name: Age: Occupation: Address: city: State: Zip code: cellphone :

attachments: EMPLOYMENT!!! (PART TIME JOB OPPORTUNITY FOR STUDENTS) (1) (3).pdf
body: EMPLOYMENT!!! (PART TIME JOB OPPORTUNITY FOR STUDENTS) I am Dr. Mark hatkin and I am a Disability Specialist and Associate Director for the Department of Disability Resources and Educational Services (DRES). I provide individual and group therapy, coaching, assessment and academic screenings to support students with disabilities(physical, chronic, psychiatric, and invisible)registered with DRES. A large percentage of the students served by the mental health unit have psychiatric disabilities or co-morbid psychiatric disabilities and need mental health support to be successful at the university. In addition, many university students with academic difficulties and no prior diagnosis are seen and assessed through the academic screening and assessment process. I also am the director of supervision, training and coordination of counseling psychology and clinical psychology graduate students of the United States who have practicums at DRES and APA-accredited school psychology pre- doctoral interns. This job offer is for you to assist me in carrying out some pending and piled up work, and to help Students with disabilities frustrated with ignorance and lack of services but as my temporary personal assistant. I care about Animal Welfare, Arts and Culture, Children, Civil Rights and Social Action,Education, Environment, Disaster and Humanitarian Relief, Social Services and lots more. This is a very simple employment. You will only help me Mail letters, Make payments at the bank or Walmart and purchase some Items when needed. This employment only takes 3 hour a day and 3 times a week for $450 weekly. I am unable to meet up for an interview because I am currently away and helping the disabled students in Italy. You will be paid in advance for all tasks and purchases to be done on my behalf and some of my personal letters and mails will be forwarded to your residence or nearby post office for you to pick up at your convenience. Upon my arrival we will discuss the possibility of making this a long-term employment if I am impressed with your services while I am away. My arrival is scheduled for the last week of November 2020. To Apply, Please email your Full name, Address, Alternate email (different from school email) and mobile number. Regards Dr. Mark hatkin

subject: Recruitment 2019 Job Opening
body: Recruitment 2019 Job Opening · Hours: Part Time · Contract: Job could convert to full time in the near future · Job Function: Middle man · Salary : $230 weekly · Job Level: Graduate/ Undergraduate · Company: Tata Global Beverages This is a rare opportunity for an ambitious college students, Tata Global Beverages Group Ltd. (formerly Tata Tea Limited) is a natural beverages company with a focus on Tea, Coffee and Water. Is an Indian multinational non-alcoholic beverages company headquartered in Kolkata, West Bengal . We are a business with the rich heritage and huge ambition. Over 90 percent of our current sales comes from branded products and 70 per cent of our Group turnover is generated outside India. Would you like to be part of our exciting journey? Are you looking for a long term part time position? This could be the perfect role for you! Read on...... *Key Tasks:* · This is strictly an on-line pay job where you work with the buying department and liaising with our suppliers only for getting the supplies needed by our agents, you will be contacted whenever they need materials during the weekdays or you can have your own part of the work completed at your leisure time in school or at home. Daily duties would be to report to your Supervisor, who would be attached to you online, He/She we always assign logs of duty daily and you would be required to work according to instructions sent to your supervisor via your mobile text and email. · We are employing you just to reduce the workload for us and on our supplier and also to keep record of materials that are being ordered weekly. Each supplier will only order for materials once a week depending on the task he or she is to complete for that week. We respect and appreciate you. Tata Global Beverages (TGB) keeps all of your information private, if you feel like this advert is speaking directly to you, we’d love to hear from you. Revert back with the information below; Your name: Contact address: City: State: Zip code: Mobile number: Email: Current job: We will be reviewing applications on an ongoing basis and so please apply as soon as you are able so we can process your information as to consider it valid to commence working with us. body: Job Offer I am Allen Szalno Ashley I work as a clinical counselor for the department of Disability of Health and Human Services (DHHS). I provide individual and group therapy, coaching, assessment and academic screenings to support students with disabilities (physical, chronic, psychiatric, and invisible) registered with DHHS. A large percentage of the students served by the mental health unit have psychiatric disabilities or co-morbid psychiatric disabilities and need mental health support to be successful at the university. In addition, many University of students with academic difficulties and no prior diagnosis are seen and assessed through the academic screening and assessment process. I also am the director of supervision, training and coordination of counseling psychology and clinical psychology graduate students of the United States who have practicums at DHHS and APA-accredited school psychology pre-doctoral interns. You have received this email because you have an offer from the University Office for Students with Disabilities to work with me while we help Students with disabilities frustrated with ignorance and lack of services as my temporary personal assistant. I care about Animal Welfare, Arts and Culture, Children, Civil Rights and Social Action,Education, Environment, Disaster and Humanitarian Relief, Social Services and lots more. This is a very simple employment. You will only help me Mail letters, Make payments at Walmart and purchase some Items when needed. This employment only takes an hour a day and 3 times a week for $320 weekly. I am unable to meet up for an interview because I am currently away and helping the disabled students in Australia. You will be paid in advance for all tasks and purchased to be done on my behalf and some of my personal letters and mails will be forwarded to your residence or nearby post office for you to pick up at your convenience. Upon my arrival we will discuss the possibility of making this a long- term employment if IÊ¼m impressed with your services while I am away. My arrival is scheduled for the last week of December 2020. I got your email through a short list from the Human Resources department to give out jobs to few students in your university. To Apply, Please email your Full name, Age, Address, Alternate email (different from school email) and mobile number Regards, Dr. Allen Szalno Ashley.

subject: External job opening: Middleman
body: External job opening: Middleman Job Summary: There’s a vacancy for a middleman position in our company. Maine Beer Company is recruiting new employees to the company for the post of a middleman to reduce the workload on the company’s suppliers. The core function of the middleman is to serve as an intermediary between the company and the suppliers. Each middleman will receive a remittance every Wednesday of the week which consists of the payment for the suppliers to make orders on available raw materials and your weekly wages. Note: Every transaction must be recorded. This is strictly an online pay job where you can have your own part of the work completed at your leisure time at home. The Company: Since day one here at Maine Beer Company, we wanted to do things right, no matter what. It is because of all those who buy our beers and all of the great people working with us that we are able to actually make “do what’s right” happen. Maine Beer Company is always striving to be better at making quality beer and taking care of our earth and the creatures living on it. Wages • A reasonable wage of 300 dollars. • An offer to make extra 30 - 50 dollars. Requirements 1. Excellent organizational, oral and written communication skills. 2. Must be good at taking note. 3. Time management abilities. 4. Positive attitude. If you care to proceed with the job, get back to us and forward your information listed below to admin.mainebeercompany@mailsystems.org : Full Name: Age: Occupation: Address: city: State: Zip code: cellphone :

subject: We are looking for a middleman
body: We are looking for a middleman Fort Garry Brewing Company is a producer, marketer and distributor of craft beers and a producer of cider, which is also a leading brand which offers incorporation services to our clients all over the globe. We are looking for a very trustworthy, hardworking and responsible individual with a weekly wage of 300 Dollars. We have agents that are working for us, these agents need materials like grains, yeast and hops to do their daily job and we need you to work as a middleman to help the agents in getting their respective supplies. You will be contacted whenever they need materials, it will be your duty to work with the supplier to make orders for the materials. Each supplier will only order for materials once a week depending on the task he or she is to complete for that week. We are employing you just to reduce the workload for us and on our supplier and also to keep record of materials that are being ordered weekly. This is strictly an online pay job where you work with suppliers only for getting the supplies needed by our agents during the weekdays or you can have your own part of the work completed at your leisure time at home. This takes 2-3 hours per week. If you care to proceed with the job, get back to us with the information listed below so we can process your information. We will be waiting for your response. NAME: ADDRESS: CITY: STATE: ZIPCODE: PHONE NUMBER: AGE:
